Alembic environment for business-platform-api

To create a migration use the alembic CLI. Example:

    py -3 -m alembic revision --autogenerate -m "initial"

To apply migrations:

    py -3 -m alembic upgrade head

The env.py reads the SQLALCHEMY_DATABASE_URI from `src.main.app` so Alembic runs against the same DB as the Flask app.
